Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心哦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集 這身...連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與面麻穿的那件很像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼會穿成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去像是不要緊麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你好好看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 不要過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一次機會 如果錯過這次的話 肯定再也...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 看上去像面麻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看見面麻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看上去像面麻麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集 真的能看見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天面麻的死都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有對面麻說那些話 面麻就不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我害死了面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說面麻顯靈的話 應該是在我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是懲罰還是詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都應該出現在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 面麻卻沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我面前出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以面麻已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論哪裡都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻說「我在這裡」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻說「謝謝你的髪夾 雪集」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 「對不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 雖然不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這麼讓他走沒有關系嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道了 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點覺察到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久之前要我陪他一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝作若無其事的給女朋友挑禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了女孩子穿的 白色的 系有蝴蝶結的連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口的膿還是處理掉比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那家夥的心都潰爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都處理掉就什麼也不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髪夾 謝謝 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等啊 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我不會停下 仁碳要走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種家夥讓他走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻才不是醜女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻是... 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這個很適合面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分適合我最喜歡的面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳要走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻要去追仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著眼鏡會不會不好看了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 面...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面...麻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個健醬拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來最近都沒有看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去買
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用特意去買啦 吃家裡有的東西就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻出現在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在雪集身邊 而是在我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈也好 幻想也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻逃避思考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家在一起很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和仁碳在一起很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想不去思考也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中某處是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻她為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家夥 太受歡迎了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有健醬拉面 這些作為補償
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為補償有這麼多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 我有話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話要說?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個棒冰要化掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能幫面麻實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是也以自己的方式在做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 有很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不像雪集那樣鑽牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間管你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊 准備舉辦聚會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 棒冰 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來一根沒關系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 還說我很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙個什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯 上網 睡覺 打遊戲 睡覺 吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是重複這些而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五話 隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 之後直接坐電車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束打工後大約七點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鳴子能過來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經把你算進去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件被拒絕的時候都不知道怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遼君真的生氣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和遼君沒有關系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的最近鳴子人緣不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在想是不是不要跟你做朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 春菜的玩笑太傷人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我們談到智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是說在考試中取得高分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是在學校取得好的課業成績
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是一個方面車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下一班是30分鍾後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是和平常一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常的讓人感覺不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想讓我怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我臭罵你一頓女裝男什麼的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 或許那樣會更感激你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要為了平衡你個人的自戀心理而利用別人好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 才讓我很多事都堅持到底 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在短信裡寫了喜歡你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意乘電車出了城 還背了個大的購物袋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是換衣服吧 和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不換一下衣服什麼的 是過不去的 在各種方面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱的真好 厲害厲害厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:14:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個換小涼了 快點歌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要發出這麼邪惡的聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小涼 什麼都可以啦 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}點什麼呢… 冷靜點啊小涼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩的開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你很勉強的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有勉強...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們兩個開溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我和小鳴先離開下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴看起來有些不舒服 我明早也要早起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要看one piece
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one piece是後天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子 之後要彙報哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 車站在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為...一起去車站...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是的呢 開溜是那個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我感覺真的有點喝多了 所以想休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是騙人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的身體不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一起去休息不就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是休息什麼的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 one piece不看了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one piece不是後天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？你不是自己說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在裝什麼呀 反正也是髒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...討厭 討厭 住手 別碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啊...放開我 放開我 你這家夥 放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要去宿海那邊去玩 你也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大家 來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 這算什麼把戲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫被男人纏住的女孩脫身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說不定是我這一生中做的最好的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助是說剛才那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是應該揍他一頓再帶我走的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我頭腦和長相都很好 但很遺憾我腕力不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 你可真夠可以的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想被你說教 你這個女裝男
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是被這麼說能感覺輕松些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是處女？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有有有...有什麼問題嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著和我交往看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你...你不是喜歡面麻麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我不能接受 那樣我不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海嗎？那家夥哪裡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡好...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別不容分說的下決定 誰喜歡他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家的老大 腦袋聰明 運動神經好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是以前的事情了好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有意外的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近也是 要是把頭髪弄得整齊點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有點像Hey！Say！JUMP的小山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}Hey！Say！JUMP由10位男孩組成的日本偶像組合 小山是指山田涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚到底喜不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是很在意宿海的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻死了 阿姨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺和宿海說不上話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠進入同一所學校 說實話我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但宿海卻忘不了面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是無法忘記 一直忘不了面麻的宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集 你剛才有喊宿海的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特急列車即將駛過 請大家稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是被甩下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 pokupokupokutin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}pokupokupokutin 日本一有名拉面館 位于神奈川縣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要在我家吃飯呐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是提供山野菜了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~ 真不愧是天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}天婦羅 日本有名料理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 看起來吃得很香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你鼻子上粘東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 面麻在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻也吃天婦羅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信啊 關于面麻的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是說過了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之後也考慮過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很明白 但面麻在這裡大概不是什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有成佛 所以才出現在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成佛...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道 那 那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻啊 稍稍給我點提示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會念pokupokupokutin咒語 不是有想實現的願望嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也希望你能夠來依靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫你成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 久川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 面麻 把願望告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不僅僅在仁碳面前 也在我面前現身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:21:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個願望 面麻也想直接跟大家說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不知道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}大家一起來解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成佛什麼的...我也不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 可以不 拜托啦 大家一起想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後面麻...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒收 沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:14.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}何ページも費やして　つづられた僕らの気分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:21.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうしてか一行の　空白を埋められない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:30.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}押花のしおり挟んで　君と転がす 使い捨ての自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:37.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}忘れかけのレンガを　積み上げた場所に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:42.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}海を見渡す坂を駆け上って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}こわいくらいに青い空と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:55.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}右手にサイダー　左手はずっと君を探している
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:01:02.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}そうやって今は僕の方へ　問いつめることもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:09.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}まだ二人はすぐそこにいるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:17.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうかまたあえますようになんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:26.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうかしてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:14.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}填寫了好幾頁 我們那連綿的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:21.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}卻為何填補不了那空白的一行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:30.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}夾上乾花瓣做的書籤 與你共騎上那丟棄的自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:37.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}前往已遺忘的卻堆滿回憶的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:42.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}登上遠望海景的坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}藍得刺眼的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:55.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}右手拿著汽水 左手一直追尋著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:01:02.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}現在已沒有需要向我詢問的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:09.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}明明兩人近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:17.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}卻祈望終有一日能相見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:26.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}這是為何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}君と夏の終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:09.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}将来の梦 大きな希望 忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:16.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}10年后の8月 また出会えるのを 信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:23.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}最高の思い出を…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:39.59,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}出会いはふっとした瞬間 帰り道の交差点で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:45.43,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}声をかけてくれたね  "一緒に帰ろう"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:54.03,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}あぁ 花火が夜空 きれいに咲いて ちょっとセツナク
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:22:00.59,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}あぁ 風が時間とともに 流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:08.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}嬉しくって 楽しくって 冒険も いろいろしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:14.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}二人の 秘密の 基地の中
